---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Samantha Squires | Operations Manager | Ray White Collective"
  description="Samantha Squires is the Operations Manager working alongside Daniel Gierach and Conrad Leisemann at Ray White Collective. 10+ years in business management."
>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">
  <div style="position:relative;background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;overflow:hidden;">
    <img
      src="/_vercel/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn6.ep.dynamics.net%2Fs3%2Frw-propertyimages%2Fa665-H3373155-164932053__1758673927-230712-AMY19482.jpg&w=1600&q=70"
      srcset="/_vercel/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn6.ep.dynamics.net%2Fs3%2Frw-propertyimages%2Fa665-H3373155-164932053__1758673927-230712-AMY19482.jpg&w=800&q=70 800w, /_vercel/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn6.ep.dynamics.net%2Fs3%2Frw-propertyimages%2Fa665-H3373155-164932053__1758673927-230712-AMY19482.jpg&w=1600&q=70 1600w"
      sizes="100vw" alt="" decoding="async"
      style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 30%;opacity:0.55;z-index:0;" />
    <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(10,8,6,0.55) 0%,rgba(10,8,6,0.65) 55%,rgba(10,8,6,0.82) 100%);z-index:0;"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
      <img src="/img/samantha-squires-headshot.jpg" alt="Samantha Squires"
        style="width:160px;height:160px;border-radius:18px;object-fit:cover;border:1.5px solid rgba(197,160,60,0.5);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);margin-bottom:1.5rem;" />
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:0.55rem;">
        Samantha Squires
      </h1>
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f5d07a;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Operations Manager</span>

      <div class="hero-contact">
        <a href="mailto:samantha.squires@raywhite.com" data-cta="team_samantha_email">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          samantha.squires@raywhite.com
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="padding:3.5rem 0 6rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-8 bio-body">

      <p class="bio-eyebrow">The background</p>
      <p>With over 10 years of experience in business management and building teams, Samantha brings a strong background in operations and a genuine passion for property. She has always loved helping people, whether it's guiding clients through complex processes or ensuring every task is completed with efficiency and accuracy.</p>

      <p class="bio-eyebrow" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">Beyond the office</p>
      <p>A lifelong Brisbane resident, and a proud mother herself, Samantha is deeply connected to her local community. Actively involved in her son's school and supporting local families, she understands first-hand the importance of finding the right home in the right area. She is committed to delivering reliable, people focused service and making sure every interaction is a positive one. She takes pride in helping families make informed, confident decisions about their next chapter and her long-standing interest in real estate, paired with a results-driven mindset, allows her to support our valued clients with confidence, care and local insight.</p>

      <p class="bio-eyebrow" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">The team fit</p>
      <p>Together, Daniel, Conrad and Samantha create the perfect balance of sales and organisation within the team. Their complementary strengths ensure clients receive both expert guidance and a seamless experience from start to finish.</p>

      <p class="bio-eyebrow" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">How Samantha helps</p>
      <p>For all your operational needs, please reach out to Samantha, who is happy to help with all your questions.</p>

      <div>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Below are just some of the tasks Samantha will assist with:</p>
        <ul style="padding-left:1.4rem;margin:0;list-style:disc;">
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Preparing your home for sale and inspections</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Onboarding and listing documentations</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Launching your property across all platforms</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Contract checks and confirmations</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Seller Disclosure assistance</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Marketing and Social Media</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Coordinating property photos</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Gathering important property details</li>
          <li>Open home management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Samantha is your go-to for keeping everything running smoothly behind the scenes.</p>

      <p>So, please don't hesitate to reach out anytime. She'd love to help.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);">
        <a href="/meet-the-team" style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-gold);text-decoration:none;">&larr; Back to the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  .hero-contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }
  .hero-contact a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.95rem;
    background: rgba(10, 8, 6, 0.42);
    border: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 60, 0.4);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: #f5d07a;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  }
  .hero-contact a:hover {
    background: rgba(196, 145, 42, 0.18);
    border-color: rgba(197, 160, 60, 0.75);
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .hero-contact {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero-contact a { justify-content: center; width: 100%; }
  }

  .bio-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.9;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .bio-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin: 0 0 -0.7rem 0;
  }
</style>

</Layout>
